{"tid":1976862,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"五毛做嘢係逐個project做，一單完咗就做第二單，好易認","createTime":"2020-04-17T13:58:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-25T03:27:04.000Z","uid":171506,"like":185,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":50,"replies":[{"pid":"10599db9367c7d3b056e0da301f628ae98669863","tid":1976862,"uid":171506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T13:58:16.000Z","msg":"例如幾個月前，有人搞612基金，連開一大堆post洗版，不斷回覆不斷正評自己友post密集唱衰，但過咗果幾日，就無人再搞再提。<br />\n<br />\n正常黎講，討論區之內，唔同嘅網友，應該有唔同嘅感興趣話題，所以不應該有洗版現象。<br />\n<br />\n或者我想講某一樣嘢，但已有巴絲打開咗post，我都唔會刻意開同一個post洗版。如果唔小心撞咗題目，有時仲會自己收檔。<br />\n<br />\n五毛就唔同，不斷開同類post佔據熱門位置，因為要同老細計錢。<br />\n<br />\n同埋五毛由於有組織，通常可以好有規律咁推一個話題，例如搞完612基金，就唱下星火，然後又屈義務律師呃錢。依家對付黃店，都係一間一間咁做，背後有一個「黃店信唔過」的主題。<br />\n<br />\n如果到咗今日，仲會輕易畀人帶風向，真係人頭豬一隻。"},{"pid":"b713dbf09c9cbacbf9f4121c6439e8423f596c23","tid":1976862,"uid":245065,"like":2,"dislike":122,"score":-120,"citedBy":8,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T14:00:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9cb7d3db9288d4382d061601c9ee5279fdf17874","tid":1976862,"uid":177213,"like":68,"dislike":1,"score":67,"quote":{"pid":"b713dbf09c9cbacbf9f4121c6439e8423f596c23","tid":1976862,"uid":245065,"like":2,"dislike":122,"score":-120,"citedBy":8,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T14:00:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T14:11:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">五毛狗<br />\n我實追擊到你死為止</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ztsZ2Z1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FztsZ2Z1.png&h=61eedfa0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kLV8Wj2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkLV8Wj2.png&h=d873b7ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JrU5Yyn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJrU5Yyn.png&h=4080f8a4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"428d8465dfd8e062b8c28aa552c272128efd6121","tid":1976862,"uid